{
  "chapter": 14,
  "title": "喝一杯",
  "titleEn": "Pre-gaming",
  "topic": "喝酒、白酒文化 / Drinking, Baijiu Culture",
  "grammar": [
    "要",
    "来一杯",
    "比...还...",
    "越来越"
  ],
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话：矮中的宿舍 (Ai Zhong's Dorm Room)",
      "en": "Dialogue: 矮中's dorm room."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "来来来！大家先喝一杯再出去！",
      "en": "Come come come! Everyone have a drink before we head out!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我不喝白酒。",
      "en": "I don't drink baijiu."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "为什么？",
      "en": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "因为台湾啤酒是世界上最好的酒。",
      "en": "Because Taiwan Beer is the best beer in the world."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "第三次。今天。",
      "en": "Third time. Today."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "那是fact。台湾啤酒在国际比赛上拿过奖的。",
      "en": "That's a fact. Taiwan Beer has won international awards."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "Bro，这是白酒！中国国粹！你来中国不喝白酒就等于没来！",
      "en": "Bro, this is baijiu! A national treasure! Coming to China and not drinking baijiu is like not coming at all!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "台湾也有高粱酒。金门高粱比大陆白酒——",
      "en": "Taiwan has sorghum wine too. Kinmen Kaoliang is better than mainland baijiu--"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "天啊你能不能闭嘴喝酒。",
      "en": "Oh my god can you shut up and drink."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "来来来。干杯！",
      "en": "Come come come. Cheers!",
      "sub": "倒白酒给大家"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我真的不喝酒。",
      "en": "I really don't drink."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "一小口！就一小口！",
      "en": "One tiny sip! Just one tiny sip!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……",
      "en": "..."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "Qingqing。Please。就今晚。live a little。",
      "en": "Qingqing. Please. Just tonight. Live a little."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……只喝一口。",
      "en": "...just one sip.",
      "sub": "拿起杯子，看了看"
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "她喝了一口。脸立刻红了。",
      "en": "She takes a sip. Face goes red instantly."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "天啊这是什么？！像喝火一样！",
      "en": "Oh my god what IS this?! It's like drinking fire!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "哈哈哈！那就是白酒！52度的！",
      "en": "Hahaha! That's baijiu! 52 proof!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "52度？？这不是酒这是毒药！",
      "en": "52%?? This isn't alcohol, this is poison!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我说的。应该喝台湾啤酒。",
      "en": "Told you. Should've had Taiwan Beer."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "第四次。",
      "en": "Fourth time."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "还有吗？",
      "en": "Got any more?",
      "sub": "一口干了"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "……你干了？！",
      "en": "...you downed it?!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "嗯。不错。有点辣。",
      "en": "Mm. Not bad. A bit spicy."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "那是白酒！大部分人第一次喝白酒会吐！",
      "en": "That's baijiu! Most people throw up their first time drinking it!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "也许我不是大部分人。",
      "en": "Maybe I'm not most people."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "嗯……其实还行。后味有一种——",
      "en": "Mm... actually not bad. The aftertaste has this sort of--",
      "sub": "也喝了一口"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "痛苦。后味是痛苦。",
      "en": "Suffering. The aftertaste is suffering."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "我要说的是fruit味。",
      "en": "I was gonna say fruity."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "那是你的大脑在骗你。",
      "en": "That's your brain lying to you."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "好！Everyone buzzed了吗？走吧！",
      "en": "Okay! Everyone buzzed? Let's go!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我只喝了一口。",
      "en": "I only had one sip."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你的脸红得像番茄。",
      "en": "Your face is red like a tomato."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "那是亚洲flush！我对酒精过敏！不是drunk！",
      "en": "That's Asian flush! I have an alcohol allergy! I'm not drunk!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你好可爱。",
      "en": "You're so cute."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "他刚说她可爱了吗？",
      "en": "Did he just call her cute?",
      "sub": "对小黑说"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "他说了。她要死了。",
      "en": "He did. She's dying.",
      "sub": "笑"
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "白酒 (Baijiu)",
      "en": "Baijiu (Chinese Liquor)"
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "Asian Flush",
      "en": "Asian Flush"
    }
  ],
